            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "3 weeks ago",
            "post_text": "<p>I'm a nurse and I've seen red light therapy used clinically. Having this technology at home is a game changer. My patients always ask about my skin and I tell them about RevitalEyes. The results speak for themselves. FDA cleared gives me peace of mind.</p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/D43886CB-7997-4B70-9F4C-346EC186F60F_1_201_a.jpg",
