    "faq": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "When can I expect to see improvements?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>While the soothing heat provides immediate relief from digital eye strain, lasting visible changes take a little time. By committing to a 10-minute daily routine, most users notice a significant difference in skin firmness and dark circles within 3 to 4 weeks.</p><p>Remember, consistency is the key to unlocking the full potential of Red Light and EMS therapy. </p><p><em>Note: Ensure your skin is moistened with water, gel, or serum before wearing the device for optimal micro-electric conductivity.</em></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is the device safe for the delicate under-eye skin?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. Being an <strong>FDA-cleared</strong> instrument, it meets strict safety and quality standards. The device is engineered to deliver controlled micro-currents and soothing heat specifically to the surrounding skin, without applying pressure to the eyes themselves.</p><p>For maximum safety and comfort: Always start on the lowest intensity setting. Ensure the device sits comfortably away from your eyelids, and keep your eyes closed to fully enjoy the spa-like experience.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "How often should I use my device?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>For the best results, we recommend a relaxing <strong>10-minute session once a day</strong>. Consistency is key! Make it a staple in your daily skincare routine—whether in the morning to reduce puffiness or at night to unwind.</p><p>While once daily is perfect for most, you can safely use it up to twice a day if desired. </p><p><em>Pro Tip: Always apply a water-based serum or gel before use to fully activate the micro-current (EMS) technology!</em></p><h3></h3>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What is your return policy?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied with your results, simply return the device in its original packaging for a full refund — no questions asked. We're that confident in RevitalEyes. Over 94% of customers keep their device and see lasting results.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Can I use it with my eye cream?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely! We actually recommend applying your favorite eye cream immediately after your RevitalEyes session. Light therapy has been shown to increase the absorption of topical skincare products by up to 40%, making your eye cream even more effective. Think of RevitalEyes as supercharging your existing skincare routine.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "How do I charge the device?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>The device is fully rechargeable via the included USB cable. A complete charge takes approximately 1.5 hours and provides enough power for multiple 10-minute spa sessions (battery life varies slightly depending on your heat and EMS settings). An intuitive LED indicator makes it easy to monitor your charging status. Its cordless and lightweight design makes it the perfect travel companion for your skincare routine!</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_7": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is the device suitable for all skin types?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! The device is designed to be gentle and effective for all skin types, including sensitive skin. The red light therapy is perfectly safe for all skin tones. Because the device features adjustable micro-electric (EMS) and soothing heating modes, you can easily customize the intensity to match your skin's specific comfort level. As a standard precaution, if you have any specific medical conditions affecting your eyes or skin, please consult your healthcare provider before use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "faq_1",
        "faq_2",
        "faq_3",
        "faq_4",
        "faq_5",
        "faq_6",
        "faq_7"
      ],
